#### [NEW] [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/nicoc/OneDrive - PXL/Documenten/TriaCore AI gemini 3.1 website/src/App.jsx)
- Build all sections requested in prompt: Navbar, Hero, Foundations, Philosophy, Protocol, Visibility, Team, Security, CTA.
- Incorporate GSAP `ScrollTrigger` and standard animations with cleanup inside `gsap.context()`.

## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` to ensure project compiles without errors.
- Run `npm run dev` and visually verify the landing page loads all sections correctly.
### Manual Verification
- Visual check: Ensure it matches the "Light-dominant" aesthetic.
- Animation check: Ensure GSAP ScrollTriggers work smoothly.
- Language check: Make sure all text is in Dutch.
